14:37.841 --> 14:40.552
What do you say
we take this upstairs?

14:40.635 --> 14:43.555
This is so much better
than cheesy garlic bread.

14:43.638 --> 14:46.183
Mmm.

14:46.266 --> 14:48.643
[ Durkas ] Chocolate.
Uh-huh. Go on.

14:48.727 --> 14:50.645
Vanilla.
I'm taking copious notes.

14:50.729 --> 14:52.564
Keep goin', Mr. Durkas.

14:52.647 --> 14:55.400
