doing here?

15:20.467 --> 15:23.845
Discussing poetry. Maybe
you'll like to recite some of yours.

15:23.929 --> 15:25.764
<i>[ Ted]
I'm not gonna recite anything.</i>

15:25.847 --> 15:27.849
<i>Just admit you didn't
write the poem.</i>

15:27.933 --> 15:29.434
I don't know
what he's talking about.

15:29.518 --> 15:31.329
Get out of here before
you get your butt kicked.

15:31.353 --> 15:33.438
I'm going over there.
No, I got this.

15:33.522 --> 15:35.482
